::Aerotaur::
    "Hello again Angel Prime.  Did you really have to do that?  I was looking 
forward to another battle.  Oh well."  He turns to Teltoli.  "Hey are you 
okay?"  The heat wave from Angel Prime's blast hits him in the side.  He 
turns back.  "Quite a blast you've got there."
